OL,3,C'I want to inspire young girls': Tara
OL,4,CJones receives an MBE
OL,6,FMike Hall spent the day with Tara
OL,7,FJones and her family as she headed to
OL,8,FWindsor Castle to receive an MBE.
OL,10,FA trailblazing rugby league referee
OL,11,Ffrom Cheshire, Tara Jones, has
OL,12,Freceived an MBE for her services to
OL,13,Fthe sport.
OL,15,FThe honour comes ahead of her history-
OL,16,Fmaking match on 28th March, when she
OL,17,Fwill become the first woman to referee
OL,18,Fa men's super league game as she takes
OL,19,Fthe whistle for the Wigan Warrior's
OL,20,Fmatch against Huddersfield Giants.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
