PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774455107
OL,3,C'I want to inspire young girls': Tara
OL,4,CJones receives an MBE
OL,6,FTara Jones said: "It's the icing on
OL,7,Fthe cake for me. Since I was a young
OL,8,Fchild, taking up the whistle it's
OL,9,Falways been my ambition (to referee
OL,10,Fmen's super league)."
OL,12,FShe discussed the upcoming match with
OL,13,Fthe Prince of Wales as he gave her the
OL,14,FMBE, and she said that he was very
OL,15,Fhappy and pleased about it.
OL,17,FPrince William acknowledged that she
OL,18,Fis the first professional female
OL,19,Freferee for Rugby League in the
OL,20,Fnorthern hemisphere as he bestowed her
OL,21,Fwith the award, she said.
OL,26,@qD@YpmrD@Spn
