PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774455107
OL,3,C'I want to inspire young girls': Tara
OL,4,CJones receives an MBE
OL,6,FTara said: "To be recognised, it's
OL,7,Fsuch an honour. It's something you
OL,8,Fjust don't think is going to happen to
OL,9,Fyou.
OL,11,F"For me, it's about the wider picture
OL,12,Fof Rugby League and women's sport
OL,13,Fgetting recognised, so it's really
OL,14,Fspecial that I can be the face of that.
OL,16,F"To be receiving my MBE today, it's
OL,17,Freally special and will stay with me
OL,18,Fforever."
OL,20,FHer family went with Tara to Windsor
OL,21,FCastle.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
