PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774455107
OL,3,C'I want to inspire young girls': Tara
OL,4,CJones receives an MBE
OL,6,FHer father Brian Jones said: "It was
OL,7,Fabsolutely fantastic, that was my
OL,8,Flittle girl there in front of the
OL,9,FPrince of Wales, getting this honour
OL,10,Fthat she's achieved and been
OL,11,Frecommended for.
OL,13,F"I've never been so proud of her in
OL,14,Fall my life.
OL,16,F"She's done some things during her
OL,17,Fcareer, and in her lifetime, being
OL,18,Ffirst this and first that.
OL,20,F"But that absolutely topped the lot."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
