OL,3,C'I want to inspire young girls': Tara
OL,4,CJones receives an MBE
OL,6,FTara Jones was the first woman
OL,7,Fappointed to Rugby League's full time
OL,8,Fmatch officials squad, the first woman
OL,9,Fto referee a senior professional men's
OL,10,Fmatch in 2024, and now serves as an
OL,11,Fambassador for a new cohort of female
OL,12,Fofficials.
OL,14,FAlongside her refereeing career, she
OL,15,Fwas also the first women's rugby
OL,16,Fleague player to score a try at
OL,17,FWembley Stadium in the 2023 Challenge
OL,18,FCup Final.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
