PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774455107
OL,3,C'I want to inspire young girls': Tara
OL,4,CJones receives an MBE
OL,6,FShe was a star of St Helen's Women's
OL,7,Fteam from 2018-2024, with 14 caps for
OL,8,FEngland.
OL,10,FShe said: "I want to represent and I
OL,11,Fwant to make it inspiring for young
OL,12,Fgirls coming through that there are
OL,13,Fgeneral opportunities for them not ...
OL,14,Fyoung girls can now see that playing,
OL,15,Fcoaching, refereeing, whatever it may
OL,16,Fbe within rugby league, there are
OL,17,Fopportunities there."
OL,19,FTara's sister Stacey Courtney said
OL,20,Fshe's: "Mega proud. I don't think it's
OL,21,Fpossible to be any prouder."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
