PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774455107
OL,3,C'I want to inspire young girls': Tara
OL,4,CJones receives an MBE
OL,6,FHer mum, Lynnda Jones said: "I don't
OL,7,Fthink Tara will stop proving herself,
OL,8,Fto herself, to the community, and to
OL,9,Fthe world. She's always been full of
OL,10,Fsurprises. Very proud."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
